title: [Quiver and Release]
description: On a stained and scarred workbench, a myriad of sharp tools sit in neat rows along one side, while small glass jars of paint line the other side.  A padded stool sits nearby, and hanging from the rafters in the back is an empty birdcage.

On a stained and scarred workbench, a myriad of sharp tools sit in neat rows along one side, while small glass jars of paint line the other side.  A padded stool sits nearby, and hanging from the rafters in the back is an empty birdcage.  Just beyond the workbench is a small round door with a brass knob set into the rear wall.
